staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10000100=I really love fishing, but these days it's more fun to chat with you, mya!
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10000200=I don't know how that came about...
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10000300=But it's a good thing, right mya?
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10000400=Hey, ^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;...
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10000500=Let's go on a fishing trip around the world someday, mya!
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10000600=There are lots of really interesting places out there.
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10000700=I'm sure there are fish that haven't even been discovered yet, mya!
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10000800=Someday I'd like to introduce you to my siblings, mya.
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10000900=I think they'd like you!
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10001000=^c:1486b0;{0-playername}^c:pop;!
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10001100=It's funny, mya! The other day I was going to write you a letter and send it in a bottle...
staxel.village.character.dialogue.RiahBestFriend.line:10001200=But then I realised I could just talk to you directly instead mya!
